Package objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    Contains information about a booking, including a booking ID, film title, seat number and customer details.
    CinemaScreen
    Describes a cinema screen inside the cinema, containing an associated list of listings (films that are showing on this screen) and seats.
    Customer
    Customer inherits basic properties from User and can also make/modify movie bookings.
    Employee
    Employee inherits the basic properties of the User class.
    Listing
    Class contains a specific listing of a film, the date that the film will be shown, as well as its time of showing.
    Movie
    Defines a movie, with an associated title, image url and short description.
    Seat
    Describes key features of a seat inside the Cinema.
    User
    Generic user with email, password, first name and last name
